SUMMARY:Easter Holiday Meal at Log Cabin Restaurant
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a delicious midday meal this Easter at The Log Cabin! \nOur Sunday meal will be buffet style this year\, designed by Chef Painter\, with drinks available à la carte. \nWe are happy to accommodate parties of all sizes and have several rooms available for Private Dining upon request. If your party includes children or individuals with limited mobility\, please let us know in advance and we will do our absolute best to accommodate. \nPlease note: Parties seated downstairs and upstairs will receive family style dining.
