SUMMARY:Ryan & Friends: Laughter in Lancaster at Bird-in-Hand Stage
DESCRIPTION:Join your favorite funnyman and his friends for an entertaining tour of Lancaster that will tickle your funny bone. He and his riotous cast of characters will share their hilarious take on our unique region\, while entertaining you with their fan-favorite comedy skits and crowd-pleasing parody songs of all sorts. \nWhether you’re a first-time visitor to Lancaster County or a frequent guest\, or you’ve lived here all your life\, you’ll see Pennsylvania Dutch Country through new eyes and have a smile on your face the whole time. This fast-paced and funny show is entertaining\, uplifting and\, of course\, family friendly. \nDon’t miss this heartwarming and hilarious look at Lancaster County!
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/ryan-friends-laughter-in-lancaster-bird-in-hand-stage/
